videos.headline: It took 11 quarters but Rutgers finally scores
videos.description: After 11 quarters spanning four games, Rutgers finally puts points on the board when Giovanni Rescigno finds Nick Arcidiacono for a three-yard touchdown to cut Illinios' lead to 17-7.

videos.headline: Rutgers ends drought, then throws a pick-six
videos.description: After Rutgers finally ends an 11-quarter scoreless drought, their next possession ends with Darius Mosely making the pick and going the other way for an Illinois touchdown.
